Class OpenrdfNativeMockServiceFactory

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServiceFactory

    public class OpenrdfNativeMockServiceFactory
extends AbstractServiceFactoryBase
    Mock service reports the solutions provided in the constructor.

    Note: This can not be used to test complex queries because the caller needs to know the order in which the query will be evaluated in order to know the correct response for the mock service.
